>Description:
I'm finding the debug feature which allows one to step
through code, and have the eval results shown to be very
nice; however it's often the case that because the debugger
buttons are centered, they often obscure the result display.

It would be nicer if either the buttons could be more integrated
with the other buttons on the first button row, or alligned
to the right of the second row so as to maximize the result
display area.

Thanks, -paul-
