 And while I'm thinking about it, there's another thing which would be nice.
 
 Presently it's impossible to continue past the first of several top level
 expressions, i.e.
 
 (+ 1 2) <- and be able to continue from here
 (+ 3 4)
 ...
 (+ 5 6) <- to (or pause) here, as no parens past the first are selectable?
 (+ 7 8) 
 
 

